&gt;&gt; Shawn VanCour: I want to jump

01:43:08.660 --> 01:43:10.290
in here while the mic's being
passed and just push back

01:43:10.290 --> 01:43:12.230
against the -- it's easy to --

01:43:12.230 --> 01:43:13.530
and I actually sympathize
with this

01:43:13.530 --> 01:43:14.830
because I encounter this
all the time, right --

01:43:14.830 --> 01:43:16.820
it's easy to lament
everything we don't have.

01:43:16.820 --> 01:43:19.200
But I want to flip that on
its head and point toward --

01:43:19.200 --> 01:43:21.460
I think, one of the things that
we've heard at the conference,

01:43:21.460 --> 01:43:23.920
like, it's all of these amazing
collections we didn't know

01:43:23.920 --> 01:43:25.220
about when we came hre, right?

