How do you find out about it?

01:43:33.470 --> 01:43:38.190
How do you match the researchers
to the archives that --

01:43:38.190 --> 01:43:40.360
how do you match the
educators with these archives?

01:43:40.360 --> 01:43:43.110
So to just put a more
positive spin on this,

01:43:43.110 --> 01:43:45.060
looka t all of the
history that is preserved,

01:43:45.060 --> 01:43:47.050
let's get people using this.

01:43:47.050 --> 01:43:51.500
&gt;&gt; You may be able to
stop kicking yourself.

